OL,3,CFans in tears as Arsenal are crowned
OL,4,CPremier League champions
OL,6,FFans were left in tears after Arsenal
OL,7,Fwere crowned Premier League champions
OL,8,Ffor the first time in 22 years after
OL,9,FManchester City were held to a 1-1
OL,10,Fdraw at Bournemouth.
OL,12,FThe Gunners' long wait to add to their
OL,13,F13 top-flight titles was ended when
OL,14,FPep Guardiola's side dropped points in
OL,15,Ftheir penultimate match, the game in
OL,16,Fhand they had over their rivals.
OL,18,FIt left Arsenal with an unassailable
OL,19,Flead at the top and kicked off the
OL,20,Fcelebrations in north London.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/15
