OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1779872675
OL,3,CFans in tears as Arsenal are crowned
OL,4,CPremier League champions
OL,6,FMikel Arteta's side will formally be
OL,7,Fpresented with the trophy on Sunday
OL,8,Fafter their final match of the season
OL,9,Fat Crystal Palace.
OL,11,FThey could still make it an historic
OL,12,Fdouble for the club as they chase
OL,13,Ftheir first Champions League title in
OL,14,Fthe final against Paris St Germain
OL,15,Flater this month.
OL,17,FThe league title ended a six-year
OL,18,Fperiod without a trophy and is
OL,19,FArteta's second major honour in charge
OL,20,Fafter the 2020 FA Cup victory.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/15
