OL,3,CFans in tears as Arsenal are crowned
OL,4,CPremier League champions
OL,6,FMidfielder Declan Rice posted a
OL,7,Fpicture on Instagram with his team-
OL,8,Fmates with the caption "I told you
OL,9,Fall.. it's done."
OL,11,FFormer Gunners boss Arsene Wenger, who
OL,12,Fled the team to their last title, in
OL,13,F2004, featured in a celebratory post
OL,14,Ffrom the Gunners on their X account.
OL,16,FHe said: "You did it. Champions go on
OL,17,Fwhen others stop. This is your time.
OL,18,FNow, go on and enjoy every moment."
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@QO]xD@JOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/15
