OL,3,CFans in tears as Arsenal are crowned
OL,4,CPremier League champions
OL,6,FFormer England goalkeeper David
OL,7,FSeaman, who made more than 400
OL,8,Fappearances for Arsenal between 1990
OL,9,Fand 2003, said on X:
OL,11,FManchester City manager Pep Guardiola,
OL,12,Fwho had Arteta as his assistant for
OL,13,Ftwo of City's Premier League titles,
OL,14,Fpaid tribute to his Gunners
OL,15,Fcounterpart.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
