OL,3,CFans in tears as Arsenal are crowned
OL,4,CPremier League champions
OL,6,F"We were close. On behalf of everyone
OL,7,Fat Manchester City, we congratulate
OL,8,FMikel and all the staff, players and
OL,9,Ffans on winning the Premier League,"
OL,10,Fhe told Sky Sports. "They deserve it,
OL,11,Ffor so much hard work and effort."
OL,13,FFormer Arsenal striker Alan Smith, a
OL,14,Ftwo-time title-winner, said he was
OL,15,Fthrilled to see his former club
OL,16,Ffinally get over the line after
OL,17,Fseveral near misses in recent seasons.
OL,19,FSmith said on Sky Sports: "Brilliant,
OL,20,Fbrilliant, fully deserved.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@dO]rD@UOUsD@bO]{D@[OU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/15
