PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1779872675
OL,3,CFans in tears as Arsenal are crowned
OL,4,CPremier League champions
OL,6,F"Obviously, they've had their moments
OL,7,Fin the last few seasons where they've
OL,8,Fcome second, but you deserve to win it
OL,9,Fif you finish top.
OL,11,F"They've had the best defence. They
OL,12,Fhaven't had the best attack ` you'd
OL,13,Fprobably say City have got the best
OL,14,Fattack ` but, as an overall unit,
OL,15,FMikel Arteta's done brilliantly well.
OL,16,FI'm really pleased for my old club."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@dO]
