OL,3,CFans in tears as Arsenal are crowned
OL,4,CPremier League champions
OL,6,FMartin Keown, a member of Wenger's
OL,7,Fthree title-winning sides, posted on
OL,8,FX: "Congratulations to this group for
OL,9,Fbecoming champions! A beautiful
OL,10,Fmoment. Come on the @Arsenal! Enjoy,
OL,11,Frest and let's go and win our first
OL,12,Fchampions league!"
OL,14,FArsenal-supporting Prime Minister Sir
OL,15,FKeir Starmer wrote on X: "22 long
OL,16,Fyears for the Arsenal. But finally,
OL,17,Fwe're back where we belong. Champions!"
OL,26,@pD@DOUtD@RO]wD@ZOUyD@gO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/15
