OL,3,CFans in tears as Arsenal are crowned
OL,4,CPremier League champions
OL,6,FPresenter Piers Morgan also referenced
OL,7,F"22 years of hurt and pain" in a
OL,8,Fseries of posts on X, writing: "5
OL,9,Ftimes the bridesmaid. Tonight,
OL,10,Ffinally, THE BRIDE."
OL,12,FHow did they do it? Here are six key
OL,13,Ffactors which have propelled Arsenal
OL,14,Fback to the top.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@[O]pD@`OUrD@TO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
