FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1779872675
OL,3,CFans in tears as Arsenal are crowned
OL,4,CPremier League champions
OL,6,FArsenal bankrolled their support for
OL,7,FMikel Arteta by spending more than
OL,8,F#250million in signing eight new
OL,9,Fplayers last summer. Spearheaded by
OL,10,Fnew sporting director Andrea Berta,
OL,11,FViktor Gyokeres became the club's
OL,12,Fmarque signing, and although he has
OL,13,Ffaced criticism along the way, his
OL,14,Freturn of 21 goals has answered the
OL,15,Fneed for a prolific scorer. Eberechi
OL,16,FEze's provided moments of magic, while
OL,17,FMartin Zubimendi has, until very
OL,18,Frecently, been a permanent fixture in
OL,19,Fmidfield. Christian Mosquera, a snip
OL,20,Fat #13million, and loan signing Piero
OL,21,FHincapie have enforced Arsenal's
OL,22,Falready impressive backline. Declan
OL,23,FRice's arrival from West Ham for a
OL,24,Fclub-record fee of #100m in 2023 has
OL,25,Fproved invaluable.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1779872675
OL,3,CFans in tears as Arsenal are crowned
OL,4,CPremier League champions
OL,6,FAfter finishing runners-up for the
OL,7,Fpast three seasons, and without a
OL,8,Ftrophy since 2020, Arsenal's mental
OL,9,Fstrength has faced a stern
OL,10,Fexamination. After they lost the
OL,11,FCarabao Cup final to City, and were
OL,12,Fthen eliminated from the FA Cup by
OL,13,FSouthampton, before surrendering their
OL,14,Flead of the Premier League, Arteta's
OL,15,Fmen were accused of "bottling" their
OL,16,Ftrophy aspirations. A City fan goaded
OL,17,Ftheir rivals by 'drinking' out of an
OL,18,FArsenal-branded bottle, while the
OL,19,Ftaunts on social media were even
OL,20,Flouder. But Arsenal's players were
OL,21,Fable to block out the external noise
OL,22,Fand have the last laugh.
OL,26,@wD@UOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
