PN,40811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1779872675
OL,3,CFans in tears as Arsenal are crowned
OL,4,CPremier League champions
OL,6,FArsenal boast the meanest backline in
OL,7,Fthe league, conceding 26 goals ` seven
OL,8,Ffewer than City ` while keeping 19
OL,9,Fclean sheets. David Raya's arrival
OL,10,Ffrom Brentford to replace Aaron
OL,11,FRamsdale went down like a damp squib
OL,12,Fat the time. But Raya has taken
OL,13,FArsenal to another level by producing
OL,14,Fa number of match-winning saves to
OL,15,Fcement his status as one of the
OL,16,Fworld's very best stoppers. Gabriel
OL,17,Fand William Saliba are developing as
OL,18,Fone of the finest centre-back pairings
OL,19,Fthe league has seen. The arrival of
OL,20,Fdefence coach Gabriel Heinze last
OL,21,Fsummer has clearly had the desired
OL,22,Fimpact. Arsenal's ill-discipline also
OL,23,Fcost them last season. But they have
OL,24,Fnot received a single red card so far.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1779872675
OL,3,CFans in tears as Arsenal are crowned
OL,4,CPremier League champions
OL,6,FUnder the stewardship of Nicolas
OL,7,FJover, Arsenal have become the set-
OL,8,Fpiece masters. Kai Havertz's winning
OL,9,Fgoal against Burnley was their record-
OL,10,Fextending 18th from a corner in a
OL,11,Fleague this season ` accounting for 26
OL,12,Fper cent of their 69 strikes ` with a
OL,13,Ffurther five goals coming from free-
OL,14,Fkicks. Arsenal have scored only 41
OL,15,Ftimes from open play, which will be
OL,16,Fthe lowest by a Premier League winner,
OL,17,Funless they can put five past Crystal
OL,18,FPalace to match Leicester's 2016 tally
OL,19,Fof 46, on the final day.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
