PN,40813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1779872675
OL,3,CFans in tears as Arsenal are crowned
OL,4,CPremier League champions
OL,6,FAfter taking the job, Arteta made
OL,7,Ftransforming the Emirates Stadium and
OL,8,Fre-connecting a disillusioned fanbase
OL,9,Fone of his top priorities. Arteta was
OL,10,Fintegral in introducing Islington-born
OL,11,FLouis Dunford's song, "The Angel",
OL,12,Fbetter known as "North London
OL,13,FForever," as the club's pre-game
OL,14,Fanthem. Originally sneered at, it has
OL,15,Funified the supporters and become part
OL,16,Fof the club's DNA. Rice described the
OL,17,Fatmosphere in Arsenal's recent semi-
OL,18,Ffinal win against Atletico Madrid as
OL,19,Fthe greatest ever in the Emirates' 20-
OL,20,Fyear history.
OL,26,@sD@WOUsD@aO]tD@QOUuD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1779872675
OL,3,CFans in tears as Arsenal are crowned
OL,4,CPremier League champions
OL,6,FArteta's lack of silverware and
OL,7,Fobscure methods ` whether by using a
OL,8,Flightbulb to motivate his side,
OL,9,Fblaring "You'll Never Walk Alone" out
OL,10,Fin training ahead of a trip to
OL,11,FAnfield, or tasking his players to
OL,12,Fhold pens in a bizarre drill ` has
OL,13,Fleant itself to criticism. So too, his
OL,14,Fside's over-reliance on set-pieces,
OL,15,Fand his touchline antics. But the
OL,16,Fproof is in the pudding, and 2,342
OL,17,Fdays after landing the job, Arteta has
OL,18,Ffinally overseen Arsenal's first title
OL,19,Fin 22 years. And with a Champions
OL,20,FLeague final against Paris St Germain
OL,21,Fon May 30, Arteta could make history
OL,22,Fby becoming the first Arsenal manager
OL,23,Fto deliver on Europe's grandest stage.
OL,24,FThe Spaniard's contract is due to
OL,25,Fexpire in 2027 but an extension this
OL,26,Fsummer is a formality.
OL,26,@qD@IOUqD@aO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/15
